{"tid":488433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"假設你同女朋友啪啪啪個陣 你識唔識掹返出黎？","createTime":"2017-12-03T16:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T02:15:19.000Z","uid":86754,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb3653489a86ac1aa5dc634bb99b2d3fa234bd8","tid":488433,"uid":86754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:52:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n我個朋友同佢個男朋友啪啪啪時候<br />\n佢個所謂男朋友<br />\n就聲稱自己<span style=\"color: red;\">唔識</span>掹出嚟射<br />\n所以就射曬係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我朋友就十分不解<br />\n係咪會識屌閪而唔識掹返出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係一心就諗好要中出？<br />\n又或者點解唔可以問一聲射係邊？<br />\n<br />\n跪求連登仔解答我朋友呢個疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n有棍亦識掹出黎射"},{"pid":"245dee9abb2782a2065fca38b9105fa44991d8b4","tid":488433,"uid":86754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f97e846f4425df5f317ec67d285e9dabc05773f","tid":488433,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"通常都係唔識插入去 你朋友個男朋友係狗黎架要射左拎得返出黎?"},{"pid":"ce6ced60df456f7639bda4fcaff5ced079de02e5","tid":488433,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:07:11.000Z","msg":"你同你朋友是咪智障？"},{"pid":"2925fb09ffdaa3d9cd4fe6a6ff9423571a1638d9","tid":488433,"uid":89931,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條仔條撚有倒鉤？"},{"pid":"2230e835f661f012e9902971d9825255bcbf9749","tid":488433,"uid":93808,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:10:03.000Z","msg":"可能佢朋友個系係黑洞"},{"pid":"ecc1affa31664365b181fc06f95e5014af7f144f","tid":488433,"uid":86754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:10